description: {"blocks":[{"key":"biaan","text":"This protocol describes the RNA extraction from human alveolar-like organoids followed by the perfomance of a RT-qPCR to quantify the amount of hostfactors (ACE2, TMPRSS2, and FURIN) of SARS-CoV-2. The protocol contains detailed steps for the lysis of human alveolar-like organoids, as wells as the RNA extraction followed by the reverse transcription into cDNA. In the next section the protocol describes in detail how to quantify the gene expression with the TaqMan gene expression kit to obtain donor dependent Ct values.
